squared.

00:43:03.090 --> 00:43:05.700 align:middle line:90%


00:43:05.700 --> 00:43:09.330 align:middle line:84%
And the 1 plus m prime
squared divided by 2e squared.

00:43:09.330 --> 00:43:13.910 align:middle line:90%


00:43:13.910 --> 00:43:16.460 align:middle line:90%
So this is the final answer.

00:43:16.460 --> 00:43:20.220 align:middle line:84%
And this is the answer you
