00:43:46.230 --> 00:43:48.624 align:middle line:90%
Otherwise, it's the-- yeah.

00:43:48.624 --> 00:43:53.640 align:middle line:90%


00:43:53.640 --> 00:43:55.590 align:middle line:90%
So this m prime is upstairs.

